Title: User can get to homepage
Description:
As a user
When I enter localhost:3000 in my browser
Then I see the word "Fish Homepage"

remember to write a test!

Title: User can view a list of fish
Description:
As a user
When I visit "/"
Then I should see a list of three fish


choose any fish you want

Title: User can view details for a fish
Description:
As a user
When I visit "/"
And I click on a fish
Then I should see details about a fish

- include the full name, short description, an image, and whether it is salt or fresh water

* don't forget to write a test!
* wikipedia is a good place to go to get fish facts

Title: User can return to the home page
Description:
As a user
When I click a fish
And the click "Homepage"
Then I should be back on the homepage

Title: User can create a new fish
Description:
As a user
When I visit "/"
And I click "New Fish"
And I fill in the fish information
And I click "Create Fish"
Then I should see a page with the new fish information
And when I click "Homepage"
Then I should see the fish listed

Title: User can search fish
Description:
As a user
When I visit "/"
And I enter a fish name into the search field
And I click "Search"
Then I should be taken to the fish page whose name matches the search query

Title: User sees not found page when searching for a fish that doesn't exist
Description:
As a user
When I search for a fish that doesn't exist
Then I should see a "Not Found" page
